reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good for price
reviews.reviewText: My daughters and I were going to visit family in another country while also exploring the different cities. We checked in and out of 10 different hotels. I purchased a set of the packing cubes for each of us. This was our first trip out of the country and I'm very pleased with this purchase. With the packing cubes and storage bags, we were able to organize our clothing and items in each hotel which can be chaotic when checking in and out of a hotel every few days. Having packing cubes also putes a little ease on packing. If I were to consider purchasing packing cubes the next time, I probably would go with the compression ones. But the cost was very good with this brand and I loved the different sizes of packing cubes in the set. Would recommend.
